text:
Dr. Wooten confirms that there are only 6 purely COVID-19 deaths in San Diego County, and that we are relying on the state's guidelines to reopen businesses.

She said most of the deaths "do have underlying medical conditions because they are older"

More: https://t.co/0Oayd27Dbd https://t.co/eRFk7SOWuW
